headline: A Fresh Look at Cboe Global Markets (CBOE) Valuation After Recent Share Price Momentum
summary: Cboe Global Markets (CBOE) has caught the attention of investors recently, with its stock climbing 6% over the past month. This move has prompted a closer look at possible factors influencing the shift in sentiment and performance. See our latest analysis for Cboe Global Markets. The recent 6% boost in Cboe Global Markets’ share price over the past month comes against a backdrop of robust long-term gains, with a one-year total shareholder return of nearly 20% and an impressive 109% over three...

headline: S&P 500 Retailer Leads Five Resilient Stocks After Nvidia-Led Market Sell-Off
summary: S&P 500 components TJX Cos, Cboe Global Markets and  RTX are stocks to watch this coming week.  The stock market suffered an ugly downside reversal Thursday, with losses on the key indexes and among leading names, as Nvidia gave up early post-earnings gains.  IBD's stock market exposure guide is now at 0%-20%.
